title: Star Guardian Skins 6.20 - Missing?
body: Maybe I'm dumb, but weren't the Star Guardian skins supposed to be released this patch?  Where are they?  There are a few of us who are looking forward to these ^^*

replies.body: Normally, upcoming skins in patch notes indicate content that may be coming but it's not necessarily on the same day of the patch.  Unfortunately, I don't have any news beyond the [upcoming skin](http://na.leagueoflegends.com/en/news/game-updates/patch/patch-620-notes#patch-upcoming-skins) section of the patch notes.  Hang tight!

Rite? I bought my rp a couple days ago just so I could get Star Guardian Jinx right when 6.20 came out, but it's not available
